headline: SLB Awarded Multiple Offshore Drilling Contracts by Mubadala Energy for Tangkulo Deepwater Development in Indonesia
summary: HOUSTON, February 12, 2026--Global energy technology company SLB (NYSE: SLB) has been awarded multiple offshore drilling services contracts by Mubadala Energy, the Abu Dhabi headquartered international energy company, for the Tangkulo natural gas deepwater development and associated exploration and appraisal drilling activities in the Andaman Sea, offshore Indonesia.

headline: AI Agents and the Jobs Report Jitter: A Wall Street Balancing Act
summary: Wall Street paused its recent rally as a robust January jobs report cooled expectations for a swift Federal Reserve pivot, while the burgeoning "AI agent" narrative sent shockwaves through the software sector, creating a stark divide between winners and losers.
